casebody.data:
No. 126,

Orig.

Kansas v. Nebraska et al.

Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $145,182.45 for the period July 1, 2002, through April 15, 2003, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier decision herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 720.]
